<P ALIGN="RIGHT">Slide 4 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 8</P>

<P ALIGN="RIGHT">Slide 5 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 2</P>
</FONT><FONT FACE="Futurist"><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">&quot;Hmm.&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Bruce frowned, &quot;The numbers are all exponents of two횄짖창혗짭횂짝  a coincidence횄짖창혗짭횂짝  symmetry?&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Sasha turned to the window again; &quot;Can you match up the slides with the patient names?&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Bruce nodded, &quot;Yes횄짖창혗짭횂짝&quot;</P>

<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">When Bruce finished cross-referencing with the Hospital database for the names, the device refreshed its display:</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
