<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Sasha walked toward the machine, &quot;The machine uses artificial intelligence routines횄짖창혗짭횂짝  they're known be off on occasion횄짖창혗짭횂짝  sometimes not catching changes in a pattern until after a refresh횄짖창혗짭횂짝  you know that.  Refresh it again.&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
