</FONT><FONT FACE="Futurist"><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">&quot;Once more on my mark,&quot; she watched her timepiece, counting out a minute before shouting, &quot;Now!&quot;</P>

<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
</FONT><FONT FACE="Monotype.com"><P ALIGN="RIGHT">Bill Nillt, Mine Engineer 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 2</P>
<P ALIGN="RIGHT">Jacob Nefth, Mine Foreman 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 4</P>
<P ALIGN="RIGHT">Nell Campbell, EMT 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 32</P>
<P ALIGN="RIGHT">Russ Campbell, Miner 횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝횄짖창혗짭횂짝 16</P>
