<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">&quot;Uh-huh횄짖창혗짭횂짝  Anyone else got any ideas?&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">An assistant yelled from the far corner of the room, &quot;Sir, the chemical make-up of the virus may make the body think it was some sort of sugar횄짖창혗짭횂짝&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"></P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Fred chuckled, &quot;An living form of sugar횄짖창혗짭횂짝 ha-ha, wait until the food industry back on Earth hears about that one!  So, what do we do against this virus?  Any Ideas?&quot;</P>

